titleInfo.title: Ver sacrum
titleInfo.subTitle: Organ der Vereinigung Bildener Künstler Österreichs

titleInfo.title: Mitteilungen der Vereinigung bildender Künstler Os̈terreichs 1900-1903

mods.note: Issues for Mar. 1898 and Aug. 1898 lack volume numbering but constitute Jahrg. 1, Heft 3 and Jahrg. 1, Heft 6, respectively.

Accompanied by Sonderheft issued in 1898; Sonderheft issued in 1902; and Sonderheft (Kalender), "Gustav Klimt : XVIII. Ausstellung, Nov.-Dez. 1903 Secession Wien", and "Die Wiener Secession und die Ausstellung in St. Louis" all issued in 1903.
With 3. Jahrg. (1900) the magazine becomes the Mitteilungen der Vereinigung bildender Künstler Österreichs, retaining, however, the title Ver sacrum.
